He is also the spiritual director of the Comunidad Budista Zen Jardín de Luz" in [[Spain]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zenluz.org/ |title=Comunidad Budista Zen Jardín de Luz |publisher=Zenluz.org |accessdate=2013-09-01}}</ref>
